Simulations


Horowitz (2011) - Replication and simulations

URL: https://louissirugue.github.io/Horowitz-2011-Replication-Simulations/Horowitz_2011.html

Github repo: https://github.com/LouisSirugue/Horowitz-2011-Replication-Simulations

Description: Replicates the paper Applied Nonparametric IV Estimation (Horowitz, 2011) on R and simulates the behavior of the proposed estimator when relaxing core assumptions

Directotree

URL: https://louissirugue.github.io/directotree/package.html

Github repo: https://github.com/LouisSirugue/directotree

Description: Represents the content of a directory as an interactive collapsible tree. Offers the possibility to assign a text (e.g., a Readme.txt) to each folder (represented as a clickable node), so that when the user hovers the pointer over a node, the corresponding text is displayed as a tooltip.
